                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6374" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1001</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8864 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">负债累累难自救 汇源果汁怎解愁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial crisis of China Huiyuan Juice Group Limited</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐文秀，黄晓娥，黄莹，杨淋茜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇源饮料食品集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务危机；汇源果汁；多元化经营</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial crisis; Huiyuan juice; Diversification operation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22021 年 1 月 18 日，汇源果汁黯然退市，同年 7 月，汇源被强制执行超 15 亿元，后又传出“破产重组”的消息。作为曾经家喻户晓的老牌果汁，汇源在停 牌接近三年后，最终走到了被迫退市的这一步。从与可口可乐并购案失败之后， 汇源果汁出现持续亏损，而其后期激进的多元化经营不仅未扭亏为盈反而因其盲 目扩张导致资金链断裂，资产负债率不断攀升；2017 年被爆出巨额债务，后又 违约贷款，深陷财务危机；虽积极寻找解决方案但始终无法摆脱财务困境，最终 被停牌退市。本案例详细讲述了汇源果汁集团陷入财务危机的过程，分析多元化 经营对财务危机的产生具有哪些影响以及在多元化经营下财务危机产生的原因， 从而引发学生对同行业上市公司财务危机的防范以及陷入财务危机如何脱困的 问题的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On January 18, 2021, Huiyuan juice was delisted. In July of the same year, Huiyuan was forced to execute more than 1.5 billion yuan, and the news of &quot;bankruptcy reorganization&quot; came out later. Huiyuan, once a household name, was forced to delist after being suspended from trading for nearly three years. After the failure of the merger with Coca-Cola, Huiyuan Juice continued to suffer losses. However, its radical diversification in the later period not only failed to turn losses into profits, but also led to capital chain fracture and asset-liability ratio rising due to its blind expansion. In 2017, he was exposed to a huge amount of debt, and then defaulted on the loan. Although actively looking for solutions, but always unable to get rid of financial difficulties, was eventually suspended from the market. This case describes in detail the process of Huiyuan Juice Group falling into financial crisis, analyzes the impact of diversified management on financial crisis and the causes of financial crisis under diversified management, so as to trigger students&#39; thinking about how to prevent financial crisis of listed companies in the same industry and how to get out of financial crisis.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理学》、《公司战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务危机的概念；识别财务危机的方法；财务危机的产生过程以及表现形式；多元化经营；多元化经营对企业产生财务危机的影响；财务危机产生的原因；财务危机的防范建议；财务危机发生后企业的应对措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
